{
  "text": "The data for the purchase cost of the equipment described in Turton et al. [CITATION_1] were obtained based on the average CEPCI (Chemical Engineering Plant Cost Index) value of 397. The updated value of CEPCI of 556.8 for the year of 2015 was utilized for the present economic estimate.",
